#: ../../storage.rst:2
msgid "存储与结果访问"
msgstr "Storage and Result Access"

#: ../../storage.rst:4
msgid "AgentSociety 2 的新实验把结果写入两个位置："
msgstr "New AgentSociety 2 experiments write results to two locations:"

#: ../../storage.rst:6
msgid ""
"**Replay 目录**： ``<run_dir>/replay/``。``ReplaySink`` / ``ReplayWriter`` 以 "
"append-only JSONL 写入 replay 数据，并在 ``_schema.json`` 中保存 dataset catalog "
"与列元数据。"
msgstr ""
"**Replay directory**: ``<run_dir>/replay/``. ``ReplaySink`` / ``ReplayWriter`` write "
"replay data as append-only JSONL and store the dataset catalog and column metadata in "
"``_schema.json``."

#: ../../storage.rst:9
msgid ""
"**本地工作目录**： ``<run_dir>/artifacts/``、``<run_dir>/agents/agent_<id>/``、 "
"``<run_dir>/pid.json`` 等文件，存放 ``ask`` / ``intervene`` 产物、agent workspace "
"与运行时元信息。"
msgstr ""
"**Local working directory**: files such as ``<run_dir>/artifacts/``, "
"``<run_dir>/agents/agent_<id>/``, and ``<run_dir>/pid.json``, which store"
" ``ask``/``intervene`` artifacts, agent workspaces, and runtime metadata."

#: ../../storage.rst:13
msgid "读取结果有三条路径："
msgstr "There are three ways to read results:"

#: ../../storage.rst:15
msgid "后端 REST API ``/api/v1/replay/...``。推荐配合前端 / VSCode replay webview 使用。"
msgstr ""
"Backend REST API ``/api/v1/replay/...``\\ (recommended, together with the"
" frontend or the VSCode replay webview)"

#: ../../storage.rst:16
msgid ":class:`agentsociety2.storage.ReplayReader`，基于 DuckDB 读取 sharded JSONL。"
msgstr ":class:`agentsociety2.storage.ReplayReader`, which reads sharded JSONL with DuckDB."

#: ../../storage.rst:17
msgid "直接读取 workspace 中的 ``*.json`` / ``*.jsonl``，用于 agent 行为分析、调试。"
msgstr ""
"Read ``*.json`` / ``*.jsonl`` files in the workspace directly for agent "
"behavior analysis and debugging.\n"

#: ../../storage.rst:21
msgid ""
"新实验不再写入 ``sqlite.db``，也不再写旧的 ``agent_profile``、``agent_status``、 "
"``agent_dialog`` 三张框架表。``agentsociety2.storage.models`` 仅保留这些历史 SQLModel "
"定义，供旧数据库兼容读取。"
msgstr ""
"``ReplayWriter`` no longer writes the three legacy framework tables "
"``agent_profile``, ``agent_status``, and ``agent_dialog`` for new "
"experiments. They remain in ``agentsociety2.storage.models`` only for ORM"
" compatibility when reading historical databases; equivalent data in new "
"experiments is stored as catalog-driven datasets."

#: ../../storage.rst:26
msgid "Run 目录布局"
msgstr "Run Directory Layout"

#: ../../storage.rst:28
msgid ""
"CLI 入口 ``python -m agentsociety2.society.cli`` 以 ``--run-dir`` 指定的目录作为实验 "
"HOME。``ExperimentRunner`` 会在其中创建以下结构："
msgstr ""
"The CLI entry point ``python -m agentsociety2.society.cli`` uses the "
"directory passed with ``--run-dir`` as the experiment HOME. "
"``ExperimentRunner`` creates the following structure inside it:\n"

#: ../../storage.rst:53
msgid ""
"当通过后端读取实验数据时，``run_dir`` 是从 ``workspace_path`` + "
"``hypothesis_<id>/experiment_<id>/run`` 组装得到的，后端会读取其中的 "
"``replay/_schema.json`` 和 JSONL shard。"
msgstr ""
"When experiment data is read through the backend, ``run_dir`` is assembled from "
"``workspace_path`` + ``hypothesis_<id>/experiment_<id>/run``. The backend reads "
"``replay/_schema.json`` and the JSONL shards from that directory."

#: ../../storage.rst:58
msgid "Replay 写入格式"
msgstr "Replay Write Format"

#: ../../storage.rst:60
msgid ""
"``ReplaySink`` 是每个进程本地持有的 append-only JSONL writer。``ReplayProxy`` 只携带 "
"``replay_dir`` 与启用标志，可序列化穿过 Ray task / actor 边界；每个消费者在本进程内 懒加载自己的 "
"``ReplaySink``，不再经过中心 SQLite actor。"
msgstr ""
"``ReplaySink`` is a per-process append-only JSONL writer. ``ReplayProxy``"
" only carries ``replay_dir`` and the enabled flag, so it can be "
"serialized across Ray task / actor boundaries; each consumer lazily loads"
" its own ``ReplaySink`` inside the current process, without going through"
" a central SQLite actor.\n"

#: ../../storage.rst:64
msgid "``<run_dir>/replay/_schema.json`` 的顶层结构如下："
msgstr "The top-level structure of ``<run_dir>/replay/_schema.json`` is:"

#: ../../storage.rst:93
msgid ""
"每个物理表写成 ``<table_name>.<shard>.jsonl``。shard 由行内容的 CRC32 计算得到， 因此跨 shard "
"的自然顺序不保证稳定；读取时应使用 dataset 的 ``default_order``、 ``step_key`` 或 "
"``time_key`` 显式排序。"
msgstr ""
"Each physical table is written as ``<table_name>.<shard>.jsonl``. The "
"shard is computed from the row content CRC32, so natural ordering across "
"shards is not stable; readers should sort explicitly with the dataset "
"``default_order``, ``step_key``, or ``time_key``.\n"

