#: ../../storage.rst:111
msgid ""
"环境模块的状态数据有两种写入路径： **声明式** （推荐）和 **手工注册** （事件流、 自定义形状）。两条路径都调用同一个 replay "
"writer，注入逻辑由 ``AgentSociety`` / 环境 router 完成。"
msgstr ""
"Environment-module state data can be written through two paths: **declarative** "
"(recommended) and **manual registration** for event streams and irregular shapes. Both "
"paths call the same replay writer; injection is handled by ``AgentSociety`` / the "
"environment router."

